{"type": "article", "id": 18593, "title": "充气球椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-07T07:52:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115155GZbir4dC125faNt6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些像充气球一样的椅子是可以真正坐上去的，首尔的设计师 seungjin yang 将吹好的气球固定成座椅的样子，然后在气球表面倒上了环氧树脂，经过 8 次倾倒后它拥有了能够让人坐下来的硬度，并保持了原本的形态与很高的亮度，更适合年轻人。因为气球的材料，让它可以随意卷成各种形状，有很强的可塑性，<a href=\"http://www.seungjinyang.com\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151535r1REmy4s6JVotfp.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"472\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115153Hln4TZBhSCkpDuUQ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"556\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115154A6iND2HSzZT1IxR7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70171149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115154jEy0oKCOekWqMlTU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"689\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84229829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151554wcTnd6PZoaYe8pC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"666\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81418093\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}